			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The broom is one of the components for the magician's focus item.  It can be substituted for the brooms that drop in Najena.  <BR>
<BR>
The four parts for the magician's broom (Broom of Trilon)focus item are:<BR>
<BR>
A Star Ruby. <BR>
A Feather from a Griffon. <BR>
A Broom from a Magician in Najena. <BR>
Toes of a Cyclops. <BR>
<BR>
If you are not going to complete the magician's quest I know of no value of collecting a broom.
				</font>
